        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Munidopsis alcocki sp. nov., male holotype, cl 13.6 mm, pcl 10.1 mm (AM P2701). (A) dorsal habitus; (B) carapace, right lateral view; (C) right antenna and antennule, ventral view; (D) right basal antennular article, lateral view; (E) right maxilliped 3; (F) right crista dentata; (G) right cheliped finger tips, ventral view; (H) right cheliped ischiomerus, lateral view; (I) right ischiomerus, mesial view; (J) sternal plastron; (K) telson. Scale: A, B, G–I = 2.0 mm; C–F, J, K = 1.0 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4684687/files/figure.png" .
